The developers have done a good deed making this game available on Google Play, the world is now a better place. This converted pc games works perfectly (unlike all the Humongous apps, sadly). There are no differences between this app and the pc version, despite on reviewer claiming it's "just the story" (whatever that means, I suspect they didn't remember the game right). Hopefully more of these good quality old games will fill the play store, much more fun and developed than the modern games.
